Package: commecometrics
Title: Ecometric Models of Traitâ€“Environment Relationships at the Community Level
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maria A.", "Hurtado-Materon", email = "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3966-5478"))
Description: Provides a framework for modeling relationships between functional traits and both quantitative and qualitative environmental variables at the community level. The package includes tools for trait binning, likelihood-based environmental estimation, model evaluation, fossil projection into modern ecometric space, and result visualization.
